  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:10pt;COLOR:black\">這條黑色皮製圍裙上沾滿了無法被去除的血跡。著裝此圍裙時，你獲得如下增益：</span><br style=\"WORD-SPACING:0px;ORPHANS:2;WIDOWS:2;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial\" /><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:10pt;COLOR:black\">你每輪有一次機會為使用武器所造成的近戰攻擊傷害重擲傷害骰，且你必須接受新的結果。</span><br style=\"WORD-SPACING:0px;ORPHANS:2;WIDOWS:2;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial\" /><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:10pt;COLOR:black\">你的揮砍武器攻擊在擲出</span><span class=\"1\">19 </span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:10pt;COLOR:black\">或</span><span class=\"1\">20 </span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:10pt;COLOR:black\">時即可造成重擊。</span><br style=\"WORD-SPACING:0px;ORPHANS:2;WIDOWS:2;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial\" /></p></div>",
